

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>My Web site</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic Reset */
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
        }

        /* Blue Top Bar */
        header {
            background-color: #0000FF; /* Pure Blue */
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .search-container {
            background-color: white;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 2px;
        }

        input[type="text"] {
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 2px;
        }

        button {
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* Layout Container */
        .wrapper {
            display: flex;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Yellow Sidebar */
        nav {
            background-color: #FFFF66; /* Bright Yellow */
            width: 200px;
            padding: 20px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: blue;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Main Content Area */
        main {
            padding: 40px;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .content-body {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .featured-image {
            width: 350px;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.4;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="search-container">
            <input type="text">
            <button type="button">Search...</button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="wrapper">
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">About us</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Contact us</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Doc</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>

        <main>
            <h1>My Web site</h1>
            
            <div class="content-body">
                <img src="project.png/250x200" alt="Solar components" class="featured-image">

                <p>
                    As the software industry moves into the second decade of the 21st century, 
                    software quality is increasingly becoming essential to all businesses and 
                    knowledge of software testing is becoming necessary for all software engineers. 
                    The course focus on the theoretical concepts of Software Testing with high 
                    emphasis on inclusion of the practical context which is equally needed to 
                    prepare the learner for the demands of this field in the workplace.
                </p>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
